NOTE: This repository contains study materials for the HERMES 2022 Foundation
certification of the Swiss Federal Administration. The HERMES method itself is
an open standard owned by the Swiss Confederation, represented by the Federal
Chancellery (FCh). The official source — and only binding reference for the
certification — is https://www.hermes.admin.ch (Digital First principle).

This repository is an independent study companion. It is NOT affiliated with,
endorsed by, or representative of the Swiss Federal Chancellery or TÜV SÜD
Akademie GmbH. Generated quiz questions approximate the official TÜV SÜD style
but are NOT certified exam questions.
